# Quality Gate Skill

Run this gate sequentially. Stop at the first failure.

## Stage 1: Lint
```bash
npm run lint --if-present || python -m flake8 --quiet || true
```
Fix all lint errors before proceeding.

## Stage 2: Type Check
```bash
npx tsc --noEmit || python -m mypy . || true
```
Fix all type errors before proceeding.

## Stage 3: Tests
```bash
npm test || python -m pytest || true
```
All tests must pass. If any fail, fix and re-run.

## Stage 4: Security Scan
```bash
npm audit --audit-level=high || pip-audit || true
```
No HIGH or CRITICAL vulnerabilities allowed.

## Verdict
All 4 stages must pass before pushing. Do not bypass with `--no-verify`.
